Interface OntopiaResultHandler<R>

Type Parameters:
R - Any type used to store result rows.
All Known Implementing Classes:
SparqlTupleResultHandler, SparqlTurtleResultHandler
public interface OntopiaResultHandler<R>

Defines interface which any RDF result handler class should implement in order to be usable by AbstractQueryResult subclass.
